fall-tuscany-italy-2-300x413.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02092059\/Elsa-Trail-waterfall-tuscany-italy-2-600x825.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02092059\/Elsa-Trail-waterfall-tuscany-italy-2.jpg 1396w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02092059\/Elsa-Trail-waterfall-tuscany-italy-2-22x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02092059\/Elsa-Trail-waterfall-tuscany-italy-2-589x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-diborrato-waterfall-tuscany\">Diborrato Waterfall, Tuscany<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Close to the end of the Elsa Trail you are rewarded with a powerful 15-meter high waterfall. The refreshing river makes it great for a swim after hiking for 40 minutes. <strong>Tip:<\/strong> When swimming into the river, watch out for the large boulders that are slightly hidden underwater.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02092109\/Elsa-Trail-waterfall-tuscany-italy-3.jpg\" alt=\"Elsa Trail waterfall tuscany italy\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Elsa Trail waterfall tuscany italy\" class=\"wp-image-64418 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02092109\/Elsa-Trail-waterfall-tuscany-italy-3.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02092109\/Elsa-Trail-waterfall-tuscany-italy-3-800x600.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02092109\/Elsa-Trail-waterfall-tuscany-italy-3-1080x810.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02092109\/Elsa-Trail-waterfall-tuscany-italy-3-450x338.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02092109\/Elsa-Trail-waterfall-tuscany-italy-3-30x23.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02092109\/Elsa-Trail-waterfall-tuscany-italy-3-163x122.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02092109\/Elsa-Trail-waterfall-tuscany-italy-3-240x180.jpg 240w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02092109\/Elsa-Trail-waterfall-tuscany-italy-3-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02092109\/Elsa-Trail-waterfall-tuscany-italy-3-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02092109\/Elsa-Trail-waterfall-tuscany-italy-3-1440x1080.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02092109\/Elsa-Trail-waterfall-tuscany-italy-3-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02092109\/Elsa-Trail-waterfall-tuscany-italy-3-600x450.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02092109\/Elsa-Trail-waterfall-tuscany-italy-3-30x23.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\