     <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>There&#x2019;s a large rock you can climb on top of and relax with the sound of crushing water.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you&#x2019;re a true daredevil: it is possible to jump from the top of the waterfall but we do recommend observing locals on how and where to jump.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Also visit: <\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/italy\/saturnia-hot-springs-tuscany\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Natural Hot Springs of Saturnia in Tuscany<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02110335\/IMG_8470-608x810.jpg\" alt=\"Elsa Trail waterfall tuscany italy\"><\/noscript><img width=\"254\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Elsa Trail waterfall tuscany italy\" class=\"wp-image-64438 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02110335\/IMG_8470-608x810.jpg 608w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02110335\/IMG_8470-450x600.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02110335\/IMG_8470-254x338.jpg 254w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-co