n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>We recommend starting at the Spugna Bridge as it&#x2019;s a beautiful walk ending at the waterfall. However, if you have little time or only want to visit the Diborrato Waterfall, enter via the San Marziale Bridge as the waterfall is right there.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.google.com\/maps\/d\/u\/1\/edit?mid=1aw1srqRE10nC7207CZ8IVbd6JLzQMNvF&amp;usp=sharing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">See the route on the map<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02110243\/Elsa-Trail-waterfall-tuscany-italy-7-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"Elsa Trail waterfall tuscany italy\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Elsa Trail waterfall tuscany italy\" class=\"wp-image-64428 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02110243\/Elsa-Trail-waterfall-tuscany-italy-7-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02110243\/Elsa-Trail-waterfall-tuscany-italy-7-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02110243\/Elsa-Trail-waterfall-tuscany-italy-7-226x338.jpg