21\/10\/02110325\/Elsa-Trail-waterfall-tuscany-italy-11-600x851.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02110325\/Elsa-Trail-waterfall-tuscany-italy-11.jpg 1354w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02110325\/Elsa-Trail-waterfall-tuscany-italy-11-21x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02110325\/Elsa-Trail-waterfall-tuscany-italy-11-571x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-parking\">Parking<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>At both bridges, there is plenty of free parking space around nearby streets however, do make sure to check if there are no blue lines on the street since blue lines indicate paid parking.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-local-bus\">Local bus<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>If you don&#x2019;t feel like making a return trip when hiking, take the local bus back from one bridge to the other. Check Google Maps for the exact bus times. Bus 135, 201, and 202 are all passing the bridges.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-best-time-to-visit\">Best time to visit<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The trail is great to escape the heat of the day with the help of the natural shade or for a nature trip and is accessible year-round. On weekends it tends to get busier with locals who come here to relax.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02110315\/Elsa-Trail-waterfall-tuscany-italy-10-564x810.jpg\" alt=\"Elsa Trail waterfall tuscany italy\"><\/noscript><img width=\"235\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Elsa Trail waterfall tuscany italy\" class=\"wp-image-64434 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 564px) 100vw, 564px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02110315\/Elsa-Trail-waterfall-tuscany-italy-10-564x810.jpg 564w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02110315\/Elsa-Trail-waterfall-tuscany-italy-10-418x600.jpg 418w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02110315\/Elsa-Trail-waterfall-tuscany-italy-10-235x338.jpg 235w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02110315\/Elsa-Trail-waterfall-tuscany-italy-10-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02110315\/Elsa-Trail-waterfall-tuscany-italy-10-113x163.jpg 113w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02110315\/Elsa-Trail-waterfall-tuscany-italy-10-125x180.jpg 125w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02110315\/Elsa-Trail-waterfall-tuscany-italy-10-534x768.jpg 534w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02110315\/Elsa-Trail-waterfall-tuscany-italy-10-713x1024.jpg 713w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02110315\/Elsa-Trail-waterfall-tuscany-italy-10-752x1080.jpg 752w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02110315\/Elsa-Trail-waterfall-tuscany-italy-10-1002x1440.jpg 1002w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02110315\/Elsa-Trail-waterfall-tuscany-italy-10-300x431.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/02110315\/Elsa-Trail-w